activities: Denison Consulting administers organizational culture and leadership surveys through its own web pages.  In most cases, personal information is submitted strictly voluntarily.  For the Denison Leadership Development Survey, the client organization submits a list of participants taking part in the survey which includes the participants’ names and email addresses.  The participants, in turn, designate and invite raters who will assess their leadership traits from their perspective by entering the names and email addresses into Denison Consulting’s web survey interface.  These names and email addresses are never made public or used for any purpose other than the leadership survey.
